1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: When a hot Italian soccer star, Gio, opens a rival restaurant next door, overworked Julie, and her inept sister, Tiffany, hatch a plan to shut him down.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Julie interviews for a position at Gio's Cafe. Julie finds it hard to resist Gio's passion and magnetism.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: On her first day at Gio's, an unexpected visitor puts Julie's plan in jeopardy. Gio and Julie's relationship heats up.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: The arrival of Gio's ex-girlfriend, Francesca, makes Julie uneasy. Tiffany's restaurant suffers another blow.

5.title: Episode #1.5
5.plot: Julie and Gio share an amazing day together. Later, Tiffany demands that Julie sabotage Gio.

6.title: Episode #1.6
6.plot: Gio and Julie relationship's reaches new heights. Francesca gives Gio an ultimatum.

7.title: Episode #1.7
7.plot: After a devastating fight with Gio, Julie is left questioning everything. Tiffany faces some hard truths.

8.title: Episode #1.8
8.plot: Julie isn't ready to give up on Gio or their romance. Gio has to make a choice.

imdb.plot outline: Accountant Julie has always been "the smart one" next to her pretty sister Tiffany. When Tiffany begs Julie to save her failing Malibu restaurant by going undercover at a successful competitor's Italian bistro, she reluctantly does - In working under an assumed identity for hot chef and restaurateur Alessandro, Julie gradually peels back the layers, gets over her fear of being seen and reconnects with her sensuality to reveal the real woman within.
